data.description: Exquisite 4-bedroom, 2-bath custom home built in 2022 on over half an acre in the sought-after Battle Farm neighborhood within the Armuchee School district. This stunning property features high ceilings, custom cabinets, a captivating custom range hood, and granite countertops. With 2,200 square feet of space, this home offers an elegant open floor plan flooded with natural light, creating an inviting atmosphere. The gourmet kitchen, complete with stainless steel appliances, is a chef's dream. The spacious bedrooms and modern bathrooms provide comfort and luxury. The backyard offers a blank canvas for your outdoor oasis. Plus, the seller may consider selling the furnishings, making it a move-in-ready dream home in a tranquil, community-focused neighborhood. Don't miss this opportunity!
